{"nodes": [{"id": "prd_qeynos_audio_suite", "label": "Qeynos Audio Suite", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_execution_protocol", "label": "Execution Protocol (one plugin at a time)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a71", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "One plugin fully finished at a time, DSP core before GUI, offline test harness catches math bugs pre-GUI. If blocked >90 min descope to docs/DEFERRED.md and move on: a working suite with gaps beats a stalled perfect plugin. Toolchain breakage takes priority over everything."}, {"id": "prd_suite_core", "label": "suite-core (shared lib crate)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Shared DSP (filters, delay lines, oversampling, STFT, pitch detector, grain engine, FDN, LUFS meter), egui theme/widgets, bus layer, and preset save/load live in one workspace crate so every plugin after the first builds faster and the suite looks like one product family."}, {"id": "prd_the_bus", "label": "The Bus (cross-plugin shared state)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Rust statics are per-DLL and FL can bridge plugins out of process, so two tiers: (1) same-DLL static Mutex<Registry> for OVERSEER Node+Master exported from one .vst3; (2) cross-DLL named shared memory (memmap2 slab in %TEMP%\\qeynos-bus) with per-slot seqlocks and block-counter heartbeats. No locks or allocation in the audio callback. Honest constraints: block-size granularity only, and Master param overrides bypass host automation/undo."}, {"id": "prd_build_ps1", "label": "build.ps1 (build/bundle/validate/install script)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_nih_plug", "label": "nih-plug (Rust plugin framework)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Pinned to a git rev; VST3 export only because FL Studio has no CLAP. GPLv3 applies to VST3 export, acceptable for a personal project."}, {"id": "prd_pluginval", "label": "pluginval (headless VST3 validator)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_template", "label": "_template (hello-gain reference crate)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74 Phase 0", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proves the whole pipeline (workspace build, egui window, FL param automation, pluginval, build.ps1) with one gain knob; kept forever as the pipeline test."}, {"id": "prd_shaper_bank", "label": "Waveshaper bank (suite-core DSP)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_stft_engine", "label": "STFT engine (realfft, OLA, Hann)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_fdn_reverb_core", "label": "FDN reverb core (suite-core DSP)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_grit", "label": "GRIT \u2014 sidechained distortion", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Deliberately first: it is the plumbing-prover for aux/sidechain input, the shaper bank, and spectral (mode C) processing reused by later plugins. Three modes: Env\u2192Drive, Waveshape-by-SC, Spectral per-bin drive."}, {"id": "prd_ember", "label": "EMBER \u2014 spectral fader / temporal smoother", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.2", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Highest risk in Phase 1 is phase handling quality (input phase while active, phase-vocoder advance for tails so they stay tonal). Descope path: magnitude-only with random phase + heavy OLA is acceptable for pads/ambience."}, {"id": "prd_impact", "label": "IMPACT \u2014 kick synth (MIDI instrument)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_tracer", "label": "TRACER \u2014 pitch-tracking multiband saturation", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.4", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Risk is detector jitter on real material; mitigated by confidence gate, median filter, hysteresis, slew, and freezing crossovers at last-confident values when confidence < 0.6 (graceful fixed-band fallback for polyphonic input). MIDI mode replaces the detector entirely."}, {"id": "prd_overseer", "label": "OVERSEER \u2014 mastering system (Node + Master)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Node and Master exported from one library (nih_export_vst3!(Node, Master)) so they share a static bus directly \u2014 one .vst3, two plugin classes. Hosting Ozone inside would mean writing a full VST3 host, explicitly deferred to DEFERRED.md. Instance label param exists because VST3 cannot read FL's track name."}, {"id": "prd_drift", "label": "DRIFT \u2014 infinity filter (Sweep clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.6", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Shepard-tone filter illusion with pure biquads; deliberately the first Phase 2 plugin because it is cheap."}, {"id": "prd_wire", "label": "WIRE \u2014 codec degradation (Codec clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.7", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Risk: audiopus build on windows-gnu \u2014 if libopus won't link, vendor libopus-sys with a cmake-less build or use pure-Rust opus-embedded. Test in the first hour."}, {"id": "prd_ouroboros", "label": "OUROBOROS \u2014 recursive processor (Recurse clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.8", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_swarm", "label": "SWARM \u2014 mass granulator (Glow clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.9", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_smudge", "label": "SMUDGE \u2014 spectral chaos (Smear clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.10", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_murmur", "label": "MURMUR \u2014 stochastic reverb (Hikari clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.11", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "FDN re-randomized per onset so every hit gets a different room; two FDN instances ping-pong with a 50 ms crossfade to avoid clicks."}, {"id": "prd_flyby", "label": "FLYBY \u2014 doppler spatializer (Transfer clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.12", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_cleave", "label": "CLEAVE \u2014 multi slicer (Slice clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.13", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_pluck", "label": "PLUCK \u2014 strummer (Strum clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.14", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_shapeshift", "label": "SHAPESHIFT \u2014 morphing distortion (Teuri clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.15", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Reuses GRIT's shaper bank \u2014 mostly a UI + morph-weights project (bilinear XY blend of 4 corner shapers)."}, {"id": "prd_chamber", "label": "CHAMBER \u2014 space simulator (Eigen clone)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.16", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Hardest clone, scheduled last. Shoebox image-source model to reflection order 3 (~60 images); descope path caps at order 2 (~25 images) if CPU-heavy. Late field from suite-core FDN with RT60 via Sabine equation."}, {"id": "prd_carve", "label": "CARVE \u2014 spectral ducker", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.17", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_nerve", "label": "NERVE \u2014 suite modulation bus", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.18", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Publishes 8 mod float streams over bus tier 2; per-param listen menus ship as a suite-core feature so retrofit is one line per param. Built after OVERSEER proves bus tier 1."}, {"id": "prd_halt", "label": "HALT \u2014 performance buffer FX", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.19", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_bandaid", "label": "BANDAID \u2014 multiband transient designer", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.20", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_patina", "label": "PATINA \u2014 analog lo-fi character", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.21", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_x_ray", "label": "X-RAY \u2014 shared analyzer", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.22", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Pure bus consumer; spectrum publishing lives in suite-core's plugin wrapper so X-RAY is essentially free (a GUI project) once bus tier 2 lands."}, {"id": "prd_chorale", "label": "CHORALE \u2014 resonator bank", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.23", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_undertow", "label": "UNDERTOW \u2014 kick-to-rumble generator", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.24", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Packages the classic techno rumble-bus routing (transient strip, saturation, small dark reverb, resonant LP, self-duck against the dry kick) into one insert; tune control locks to project key."}, {"id": "prd_seance", "label": "SEANCE \u2014 ethereal vocal machine", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.25", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_ascend", "label": "ASCEND \u2014 tension generator", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a74.26", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_rumble_bassline", "label": "W1 RumbleBassline.pyscript", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_break_chop", "label": "W2 BreakChop.pyscript", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W2", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_dark_progression", "label": "W3 DarkProgression.pyscript", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_session_bootstrap", "label": "W4 session_bootstrap.py", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W4", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_project_janitor", "label": "W5 project_janitor.py", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_sample_librarian", "label": "W6 sample_librarian.py", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W6", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Dry-run mode first, never destructive without --apply."}, {"id": "prd_reference_gap", "label": "W7 reference_gap.py", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W7", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "prd_vitalgen", "label": "W8 vitalgen \u2014 Claude-powered Vital preset generator", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75 W8", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": ".vital files are plain JSON and Vital is open source, so the full param schema is verifiable \u2014 ideal for LLM generation (pydantic schema, tool-use, validate, clamp ranges). Serum 2 deferred: binary container format needs a reverse-engineering pass first."}, {"id": "prd_fl_studio_mcp_server", "label": "FL Studio MCP server", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "prd_execution_protocol", "target": "prd_qeynos_audio_suite", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a71", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "prd_qeynos_audio_suite", "target": "prd_suite_core", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "prd_shaper_bank", "target": "prd_suite_core", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "prd_stft_engine", "target": "prd_suite_core", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "prd_fdn_reverb_core", "target": "prd_suite_core", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "PRD.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "prd_the_bus", "target": "prd_suite_core", "relation": "refe